source.name: Motor Carrier Registrations - Census File (December 2011)
source.description: Registration information on interstate, intrastate non-hazmat, and intrastate truck and bus companies that operate in the United States and have registered with FMCSA. Contains contact information and demographic information (number of drivers, vehicles, commodities carried, etc).
